These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, horse, turtle
House: craftsman, townhouse, ranch-style, victorian
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the victorian house is on the far left##1
3. the ranch-style house is between the townhouse house and the owner of the lizard##2
4. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | turtle         | lizard   | horse | frog       |
| House      | victorian | craftsman | ranch-style   | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, cola, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, blues, soul
1. the fan soul is between the person drinking cola and the fan metal##2
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
3. the fan blues is on the right of the fan classical##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | 7up | soy-milk | cola | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | soul   | classical | blues       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, satire, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, baking, hiking, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | thriller    | epic | martial-arts   | satire  |
| Hobby   | baking | hiking   | skydiving | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, drama, adventure
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person watching adventure movies##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure   | time-travel    | drama       | western   |
| Birthday   | november | july | april | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, videographer, mechanic, scientist
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, polish, nigerian, colombian
1. the security-guard is on the left of the mechanic##1
2. the nigerian is on the far left##1
3. the spanish is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is between the spanish and the polish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Job   | security-guard        | mechanic | scientist  | videographer |
| Nationality      | nigerian | polish  | colombian | spanish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
House: cottage, gothic-revival, craftsman, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, pilot, social-worker, dressmaker
1. the social-worker is on the right of the pilot##1
2. the farmhouse house is the social-worker##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the chef##1
5. the craftsman house is between the cottage house and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| House   | gothic-revival     | craftsman           | cottage | farmhouse  |
| Job         | chef | dressmaker | pilot   | social-worker |

