.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, daffodil, begonia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, baseball, rowing, soccer
1. the person who growsorchid is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who growszinnia is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who growsdaffodil##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower   | begonia   | orchid | zinnia | daffodil      |
| Sport     | rowing | handball    | baseball  | soccer |

