.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, pineapple, potato, tomato
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, may, april
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person eating potato and the person who's birthday is in may##2
3. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Food       | lettuce | tomato | potato     | pineapple   |
| Birthday   | may   | october     | april | september |

