.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, pink, light-blue, orange
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, montecristo, pall-mall, chaman
1. the person who likes light-blue is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who likes red##2
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who likes red##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes red##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person who likes red is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Color         | pink | light-blue | red | orange |
| Cigar   | ritmeester         | chaman       | montecristo    | pall-mall         |

