.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, coffee, 7up
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, azure, lilac, purple
1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
5. the person who likes azure is between the person drinking milk and the person who likes purple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage    | 7up   | coffee      | milk   | cola  |
| Color   | purple | azure | lilac | blue |

