.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, gardening, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, dancer, security-guard, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
3. the dancer is on the right of the security-guard##1
4. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby          | collecting     | singing | rock-climbing   | gardening        |
| Job   | engineer | security-guard   | dancer | police-officer |

