.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
House: modern, craftsman, art-deco, cottage
City: nizza, hannover, colone, marseilles
1. the person traveling to colone is the craftsman house##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is the modern house##1
4. the art-deco house is the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is between the craftsman house and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| House         | craftsman | art-deco | cottage | modern |
| City   | colone          | hannover     | marseilles  | nizza     |

