2. the british is between the mexican and the french##2
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the mexican is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the russian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Transport           | train | snowmobile | trike | scooter |
| Nationality   | french   | british | mexican         | russian |

