2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person driving the bus##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Transport   | jet-ski | bus | van | tram |
| Hobby           | fishing  | hiking  | singing | baking      |

