.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, scooter, trike
There 4 different types of food: mango, plum, pear, kiwi
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating plum##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person eating mango##1
4. the person eating kiwi is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the scooter##2
5. the person driving the scooter is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | trike   | airplane   | bus | scooter |
| Food         | mango | plum | kiwi     | pear    |

