.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, videographer, teacher, fisherman
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, yellow, chestnut, aquamarine
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
2. the freelancer is between the person who likes red and the fisherman##2
3. the fisherman is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the videographer is on the far right##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | teacher    | fisherman     | freelancer | videographer |
| Color     | yellow | aquamarine | chestnut       | red     |

 